Author: NuclearSpark
Text: I did similar when I was first going through restriction. Eventually it got to the point where people already expect me to not eat a lot and they assume I'm just small naturally. :-) Of course I'm full! I'm definitely not going to binge on the leftovers + 7 misc items from the fridge/cabinets at 2am, followed by purging in the shower, then finally going to sleep at roughly 7am full of self loathing and an extra bowl of cereal after purging cause I have no self control!!  What were we talking about again
